trans-unit.source: Provides an interface that can be used to optimize the reloading of a designer.
trans-unit.target: Gir et grensesnitt som kan brukes til å optimalisere omstart av en designer.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> can implement this interface to support optimized reloading by the designer.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>kan implementerer dette grensesnittet for å støtte optimalisert laste av utformeren.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: When a designer reparses a file for display, it can use this interface to improve performance.
trans-unit.target: Når en designer reparses en fil for visning, kan den bruke dette grensesnittet for å forbedre ytelsen.

trans-unit.source: To support this performance optimization method, the designer can pass a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit> that represents the document code to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ICodeDomDesignerReload.ShouldReloadDesigner%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: For å støtte denne metoden for optimalisering av ytelse, designer kan sende en <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit>som representerer Dokumentkode til den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ICodeDomDesignerReload.ShouldReloadDesigner%2A>metoden.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ICodeDomDesignerReload.ShouldReloadDesigner%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ICodeDomDesignerReload.ShouldReloadDesigner%2A> returns a value that indicates whether the code has changed and typically, whether your code should reload the designer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ICodeDomDesignerReload.ShouldReloadDesigner%2A>Returnerer en verdi som angir om koden er endret, og vanligvis om koden skal laste inn designer.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ICodeDomDesignerReload.ShouldReloadDesigner%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it is unnecessary to spend time reloading the designer.
trans-unit.target: Det er ikke hvis ikke nødvendig å bruke tid laste designer.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the designer should reload in order to import the specified compile unit correctly.
trans-unit.target: Angir om designer må Last inn hvis du vil importere den angitte kompilering enheten på riktig måte.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"></xref> containing the designer document code.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"> </xref> som inneholder koden designer-dokument.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the designer should reload; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis du skal laste inn designer; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
